node.text:
FACETIME shoot with @mommy_nannan at 3am because it’s morning in California 😂

One thing about doing face time shoot, it can be very tiring because the model have to adjust the angle & distance for you so you can snap! And at the same time you have to know how to direct your friends/models well if not it’s very awkward. But besides that, it can be a very good time to catch up on old times since we can’t travel to find our friends ~

Con side : quality can be pretty bad but I guess it trains your directing skills 😂

Taken with Amanda ‘s iPhone 8
